fields.name: B mng ty (Asparagus Beetles)
fields.characteristic:
It is important to correctly identify the two different kinds of asparagus beetles because the common asparagus beetle is found more often and causes more damage.

Both types of asparagus beetle adults are -inch long with oval-shaped bodies and moderate length antennae.

The adult common asparagus beetle (Crioceris asparagi) is bluish-black with six cream colored spots on its back.
Adult spotted asparagus beetles (Crioceris duodecimpunctata) are reddish-orange with twelve black spots.

Trc khi lt xc vi ngy, su non n t, hot ng chm sau  b xung thn cy v chui xung t   su t 2,5 n 5,0cm so vi mt t  ha nhng. fields.characteristic: Cc giai on vng i ca Scirtothrips dorsalis bao gm trng, u trng ci u tin v th hai, giai on chun b, nhng v trng thnh. Nhng con ci mp mp nht trng vo bn trong cc m thc vt pha trn b mt t. Trng c kch thc siu nh (di 0,075 mm v rng 0,070 mm), hnh qu thn v c mu trng kem (Seal et al. 2009a). Tui th ca b tr t b nh hng bi cc loi cy k ch. V d,  28  C, mt 11,0 ngy  u trng la u tin tin n giai on trng thnh trn cy h tiu v 13,3 ngy trn cy b. Tui th trng thnh ca b tr t ko di 15,8 ngy trn cy c tm, nhng ch 13,6 ngy trn cy c chua
fields.value: B tr t c mu nht v chiu di ca u trng ln th nht v th hai v nhng ln lt l 0,37-0,39, 0,68-0,71 v 0,78-0,80 mm. Con trng thnh di khong 1,2 mm vi i cnh sm mu v cc m en to thnh cc sc khng hon chnh xut hin  mt lng trn bng (Seal et al. 2009a). C rt nhiu microtrichia v cc g phn tinh th ngang sm mu trn bng cng nh xng c. Trn cc trng vi m bn ca cc loi mi bng l ba b a m. Lc sau gc trn phn on VIII  hon tt. B tr t to ra cc vt so n gy hi, bin dng l, v s i mu ca chi, hoa v qu non bng cch n cc m phn sinh ca cc u cui ca cy k ch v trn cc b phn mm khc trn b mt t. Scirtothrips dorsalis khng c bo co n cc m vt ch trng thnh. Theo Sanap v Nawale (1987), con trng thnh v nhng ca Scirtothrips dorsalis ht nha t bo ca l, gy ra hin tng cun l ln trn v gim kch thc l. V d, mt s ph hoi nng ca Scirtothrips dorsalis trn cy h tiu lm thay i din mo ca cy thnh ci c gi l "bnh xon l t". S xut hin ca cc b phn cy b bin mu hoc bin dng cho thy s hin din ca Scirtothrips dorsalis.
